    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "TWA®\nWORLDWIDE\nTIMETABLE\nApril 4, 1999\nTHA\nDOMESTIC RESERVATIONS 1.800.221.2000 • INTERNATIONAL\nATIONS\nGREAT NEW DESTINATIONS\nAND ONE NEW PLANE EVERY\n10 DAYS To TAKE YOU THERE.\nAnchorage, Alaska\nVancouver, Canada\nPortland, Maine\nEl Paso, Texas\nMcAllen, Texas\nINCLUDING TRANS WORLD EXPRESS® SERVICE",
      "FOR THE FIRST\nTRANSATLANTIC\nAVIATORS,\nTHE MISSION\nENDED WHEN\nTHE FLIGHT\nLANDED.\nTODAY, THAT'S\nWHEN YOUR\nMISSION STARTS.\nTHAT'S WHY WE CREATED TRANS WORLD\nONE, WHERE YOUR BUSINESS-CLASS FARE\nBUYS YOU OUR VERY BEST SERVICE.\nTrans World One\" offers comforts that bring the\ncontinents closer. Luxuries like plush recliners.\nSuperior legroom. A selection of multi-course\ngourmet meals, including our quick \"Expressly\nYours\"\nservice. And for a good night's rest,\n100% wool blankets or duvet comforters, and plump pillows.\nPlus, state-of-the-art in-seat entertainment, and more to come.\nTrans World One is one of the many ways we're\nrecognizing today's aviators. Because we know you're on a\nmission. And it's our mission to help you arrive ready. For\nreservations, call your travel\nprofessional or TWA at\n1-800-892-4141. Visit us online at www.twa.com.\nWE WANT TO BE YOUR AIRLINE.\"\nTWA\nNEW YORK\nROmE\nST. LOUIS\nLOndon\nPARIS\nLIsBON MILAN\nBARCELONA\nTEL AVIV\nMADRID\nCAIRO\nRIYADH"
    ],
